title: 奇迹于你
subtitle: 超高校级幸运儿
content: Spring breeze whispers secrets untold,Underneath the surface, plots bold.Murderous intent in silence grows,Mastermind behind the shadows shows.Enigma wrapped in a riddle, tight,Revealed at last in the fading light.Yielding truth that was hidden deep,Shadowed by a promise they couldn't keep.
